<B>CE Franklin Ltd. is Canada's leading oilfield supply company.  Primarily serving the producers
of oil and natural gas, the Company distributes a full range of products such as pipe, valve,
fittings and industrial maintenance supplies which are needed to efficiently produce oil and
gas.  In addition, the Company provides services for energy producers such as oil pump
rebuilding and warehouse management.</B>
